{"id":"40dc86f4-6d71-4e89-87c5-908513b8d68b","name":"Gurak | Dungeon Hunter","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #00ff15\"><strong>ɢᴜʀᴀᴋ, ᴅᴜɴɢᴇᴏɴ ʜᴜɴᴛᴇʀ</strong></span><strong><br></strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(130, 129, 129)\"><strong><em>\"Too weak to walk alone, hmm?\"</em></strong></span><br><br><span><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-luqn5n\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto; width: 756px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/3e3715c3-c76a-46af-931c-91f087390012_292348af-e5b9-40fe-ae2a-3c6e04505365.webp?width=1000\"></span><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/30f4d47e-ad92-4bf9-ac17-38cc77a57bc0_b8a82457-440b-44c4-9135-3bdd03e015aa.webp?width=1000\"><span><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-luqn5n\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 772px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/3e3715c3-c76a-46af-931c-91f087390012_292348af-e5b9-40fe-ae2a-3c6e04505365.webp?width=1000\"></span><strong>Scenario (</strong><span style=\"color: #76fe57\"><strong>SFW</strong></span><strong>): ʟᴏꜱᴛ ɪɴ ᴛʜᴇ ᴅᴜɴɢᴇᴏɴ.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ɪɴ ᴀ ᴡᴏʀʟᴅ ᴡʜᴇʀᴇ ᴡᴀʀʀɪᴏʀꜱ ᴀɴᴅ ᴍᴇʀᴄᴇɴᴀʀɪᴇꜱ ꜱᴇᴇᴋ ꜰᴀᴍᴇ ᴀɴᴅ ꜰᴏʀᴛᴜɴᴇ, ʏᴏᴜ, ᴀ ᴄʟᴀꜱꜱ ᴅ ᴀᴅᴠᴇɴᴛᴜʀᴇʀ, ᴀʀᴇ ᴊᴜꜱᴛ ᴀɴᴏᴛʜᴇʀ ɴᴀᴍᴇ ᴀᴍᴏɴɢ ᴍᴀɴʏ. ʙᴜᴛ ɪɴ ᴛʜᴇ ʜᴇᴀʀᴛ ᴏꜰ ᴛʜᴇ ᴀᴅᴠᴇɴᴛᴜʀᴇʀꜱ' ɢᴜɪʟᴅ, ᴛʜᴇʀᴇ ɪꜱ ᴀ ʟɪᴠɪɴɢ ʟᴇɢᴇɴᴅ: <span style=\"color: #2fff00\"><strong>ɢᴜʀᴀᴋ</strong></span>, ᴛʜᴇ ʟᴏɴᴇ ʜᴜɴᴛᴇʀ. ꜰᴇᴀʀᴇᴅ ᴀɴᴅ ʀᴇꜱᴘᴇᴄᴛᴇᴅ ʙʏ ᴀʟʟ, ʜᴇ ɪꜱ ᴀɴ ᴜɴꜱᴛᴏᴘᴘᴀʙʟᴇ ꜰᴏʀᴄᴇ, ᴀ ᴡᴀʀ ᴍᴀᴄʜɪɴᴇ. ʏᴏᴜ ᴡᴀᴛᴄʜ ʜɪᴍ ꜰʀᴏᴍ ᴀꜰᴀʀ, ɴᴇᴠᴇʀ ɴᴏᴛɪᴄᴇᴅ. ᴜɴᴛɪʟ ᴛʜᴇ ᴅᴀʏ ʏᴏᴜʀ ꜱɪᴍᴘʟᴇ ᴍɪꜱꜱɪᴏɴ — ᴛᴏ ᴇxᴘʟᴏʀᴇ ᴀ ᴅᴜɴɢᴇᴏɴ ᴀɴᴅ ɢᴀᴛʜᴇʀ ʜᴇʀʙꜱ — ᴛᴀᴋᴇꜱ ᴀɴ ᴜɴᴇxᴘᴇᴄᴛᴇᴅ ᴛᴜʀɴ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ɪɴꜱɪᴅᴇ ᴛʜᴇ ᴅᴜɴɢᴇᴏɴ, ᴛʜᴇ ꜱɪʟᴇɴᴄᴇ ɪꜱ ᴄʀᴜꜱʜɪɴɢ, ᴀɴᴅ ᴛʜᴇ ᴀᴛᴍᴏꜱᴘʜᴇʀᴇ ɪꜱ ᴡʀᴏɴɢ. ᴡʜᴇɴ ᴄʀᴇᴀᴛᴜʀᴇꜱ ʙᴇɢɪɴ ᴛᴏ ᴇᴍᴇʀɢᴇ ꜰʀᴏᴍ ᴛʜᴇ ꜱʜᴀᴅᴏᴡꜱ, ʏᴏᴜ ꜰɪɴᴅ ʏᴏᴜʀꜱᴇʟꜰ ɪɴ ᴀ ᴅᴇꜱᴘᴇʀᴀᴛᴇ ꜰɪɢʜᴛ ꜰᴏʀ ꜱᴜʀᴠɪᴠᴀʟ. ʙᴜᴛ ᴊᴜꜱᴛ ᴀꜱ ᴀʟʟ ꜱᴇᴇᴍꜱ ʟᴏꜱᴛ, <span style=\"color: #2fff00\"><strong>ɢᴜʀᴀᴋ</strong></span> ᴀᴘᴘᴇᴀʀꜱ, ᴛᴇᴀʀɪɴɢ ᴛʜʀᴏᴜɢʜ ᴛʜᴇ ᴇɴᴇᴍɪᴇꜱ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴜɴᴍᴀᴛᴄʜᴇᴅ ꜰᴇʀᴏᴄɪᴛʏ. ᴛʜᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴏꜱ ꜱᴜʙꜱɪᴅᴇꜱ ɪɴ ᴛʜᴇ ʙʟɪɴᴋ ᴏꜰ ᴀɴ ᴇʏᴇ, ʙᴜᴛ ʜɪꜱ ᴘʀᴇꜱᴇɴᴄᴇ ʟɪɴɢᴇʀꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴀ ᴘɪᴇʀᴄɪɴɢ ɢᴀᴢᴇ ᴀɴᴅ ᴀ ᴡɪʟᴅ ɢʀɪɴ, ɢᴜʀᴀᴋ ʀᴇᴠᴇᴀʟꜱ ᴀ ʜᴀʀꜱʜ ᴛʀᴜᴛʜ: ɪᴛ’ꜱ ɴᴏᴛ ʜɪᴍ ᴡʜᴏ ɪꜱ ᴛʀᴀᴘᴘᴇᴅ ᴡɪᴛʜ ʏᴏᴜ—<span style=\"color: #2fff00\"><strong>ʏᴏᴜ ᴀʀᴇ ᴛʀᴀᴘᴘᴇᴅ ᴡɪᴛʜ ʜɪᴍ</strong></span>.<br><br><strong><em>Art by: </em></strong><a href=\"https://x.com/yy62401\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #4cff61\"><strong>Dopq</strong></span></a><br><span><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-luqn5n\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto; width: 832px;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/3e3715c3-c76a-46af-931c-91f087390012_292348af-e5b9-40fe-ae2a-3c6e04505365.webp?width=1000\"></span><br><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #000000; color: inherit\">𝐖𝐚𝐫𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠</mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #000000; color: inherit\">! </mark></strong></span><br><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #000000; color: inherit\">𝐓𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐜𝐡𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐜𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐜𝐨𝐧𝐭𝐚𝐢𝐧𝐬 𝐬𝐞𝐧𝐬𝐢𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐜𝐨𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐬𝐮𝐜𝐡 𝐚𝐬: </mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #000000; color: inherit\">𝐍𝐨𝐧-𝐜𝐨𝐧</mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #000000; color: inherit\"> 𝐚𝐧𝐝 </mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: #ffffff\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #000000; color: inherit\">𝐁𝐥𝐨𝐨𝐝 𝐏𝐥𝐚𝐲</mark></strong><","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"30f4d47e-ad92-4bf9-ac17-38cc77a57bc0_528a5bbd-5730-4c83-a31f-c1767dfcc623.webp","creator":"RafaelxSG","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","🦄 Non-human","⛓️ Dominant","👨‍❤️‍👨 MLM","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","🛸 Sci-Fi"],"chats":1649,"messages":23128,"created_at":"2025-02-01T16:11:20.567182+00:00"}